title: RMA blanked by Greene County
text:
Saturday October 24th, 2015 2:11AM Posted 6:37AM on Saturday 24th October 2015 ( 4 hours from now ) RMA blanked by Greene County By AccessWDUN Staff Related Articles 2015 High school football rankings 2015 High School Football region standings WEEK 9: Region titles clinched, set-up in big night of prep football action VIDEO: Red Elephants' whip Jaguars, set up showdown with Loganville 
GREENSBORO — The Riverside Military football team suffered a 39-0 defeat at Greene County on Friday in Greensboro. 
The Eagles (1-7, 0-4 Region 8-AA) managed 133 yards of offense, including 98 yards rushing for Kaseem Duke 
The Riverside defense forced a turnover and blocked two point after attempts. 
The Eagles travel to Union County next Friday. Associated Categories : Sports , High School Sports , Friday Game Night Associated Tags : High school football, Riverside Military football © Copyright 2015 AccessWDUN.com
